Project: GHG Portal
Stack: Astro + React + TS + Tailwind + shadcn/ui
Deploy: github workflow + github page -> unep-grid.github.io/grid_stat

Key paths:
@ -> ./src/*

Structure:
/src/
  /components/
    /about - Team info
    /data - Explorer, charts, tables
    /home - Hero, news
    /layout - nav, ...
    /ui - shadcn components
  /pages/ - about, data, home, news routes
  /lib/ - utils, types
  /data/ - dictionaries

Config:
- React JSX enabled
- Base styles disabled in Tailwind
- MDX for content
- i18n ready

Purpose: GHG data visualization portal with multilingual support
